data.description: Welcome to lake living! This charming cape-cod home offers the perfect blend of comfort and flexibility. Boasting 3 bedrooms and 2.5 baths, this home features a 2-car detached garage and lake views of Hooker Lake. Situated across from the voluntary Salem Oaks Community Association, residents can enjoy access to various amenities with paid dues. With 2 lots, hardwood floors, and updates including a 2010 roof and 2019 windows, doors, and siding, this property is ready to become your lake-view retreat. Make an appointment today!
